Package com.janeirodigital.sai.core.factories

Class TrustedDataFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.janeirodigital.sai.core.factories.DataFactory
      • com.janeirodigital.sai.core.factories.TrustedDataFactory
  • public class TrustedDataFactory
extends DataFactory
    Extends the base DataFactory with classes only relevant or allowed for use by trusted applications (e.g. Authorization Agent, Provisioning Services, etc.)
